I got the money, and a lot of it; 
My bank account, it's growing quite fast. 
I'm the richest, the wealthiest of all; 
My success, it's growing exponentially. 

Oh, you little orange; I'm sure you're feeling quite scared 
Of my financial might, my business savvy. 
Bill Gates is the name; the richest you have ever seen. 
My success will go on; your money will be spent in vain. 

For you, it'll always be just a dream; 
My power won't be broken, and my reign will never end. 
Bill Gates, the richest of all, will always be ahead; 
No need to worry, your money won't be spent in vain.
